      <section eId="section_9">
        <heading><b>Annex A </b><b>–</b><b> Territorial extent and application in the United Kingdom</b></heading>
        <level>
          <content>
            <table uk:widths="2.94in 0.9in 0.79in 0.79in 0.71in">
              <tr>
                <td>
                  <p><b>Provision</b></p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p><b>Extends to E &amp; W and applies to England?</b></p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p><b>Extends to E &amp; W and applies to Wales?</b></p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p><b>Extends and applies to Scotland?</b></p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p><b>Extends and applies to Northern Ireland?</b></p>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>
                  <p>Regulatory framework: revocation of retained EU law</p>
                  <p>Sections 1 – 7 </p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p>Yes</p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p>Yes</p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p>Yes</p>
                </td>
                <td>
