                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>
                  <p>Regulatory framework: new regulatory powers </p>
                  <p>Sections 8 – 24</p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p>Yes</p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p>Yes</p>
                </td>
