                  <p>Yes</p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p>Yes </p>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>
                  <p>Regulatory framework: accountability of regulators</p>
                  <p>Sections 25 – 53</p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p>Yes</p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p>Yes</p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p>Yes</p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p>Yes </p>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>
                  <p>Access to cash</p>
                  <p>Sections 54 and 55</p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p>Yes</p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p>Yes</p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p>Yes</p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p>Yes </p>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>
                  <p>Performance of functions relating to financial market infrastructure </p>
                  <p>Section 56</p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p>Yes</p>
